<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .otp {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello, <%= name %>!</h2>
    <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) for verification is:</p>
    <p class="otp"><%= otp %></p>
    <p>Please use this code within the next <%= minutes %> minutes to complete your verification process.</p>
    <p>If you didnâ€™t request this, please ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you,<br>Skype-Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
